{"tid":763991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我個細佬 成個生番大陸佬咁？","createTime":"2018-08-01T14:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T15:14:49.000Z","uid":88630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c4f8dae468277cf587b55e1870a0c73140dfc355","tid":763991,"uid":88630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"屌 好嬲啊！<br />\n今日我細佬係間開住冷氣嘅房放屁<br />\n我叫佢下次出去放 <br />\n佢好串咁話：唔得喎忍唔住<br />\n跟著佢頭先叫我幫佢簽學生貸款<br />\n我要求佢以後唔準係間房放屁先簽<br />\n之後佢仲係勁串 撻啊媽出嚟<br />\n我啊媽仲要覺得冇問題<br />\n係咁幫佢叫我簽名<br />\n搞到好似係我錯咁<br />\n依家係邊個冇公德心在先？<br />\n點解你有事相求都仲可以咁囂張？<br />\n收皮啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4924fd0ec158d1dcc65a89af3195fc5c3e939098","tid":763991,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"係咪放下屁都唔得呀？"},{"pid":"3d081bfa39a2e8d0a54f432c0b87b66001fca46e","tid":763991,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁你條on9西又幫佢？</span>"},{"pid":"194200b59196925930e26df342bd765dbbeb58c1","tid":763991,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"屋企人放個屁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第時你老公瞓緊係咪都要佢走出房放屁？"},{"pid":"2e75e17ce49ab5dd994fac170e0e2a546269a1e0","tid":763991,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"臭雞收嗲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314b5db8947c30e2428e5961d231a953cb38adcf","tid":763991,"uid":88630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁你條on9西又幫佢？</span></blockquote><br />\n我點都唔會簽！"},{"pid":"acd990d94b6878db1e6a9a437e52d2564b90dc87","tid":763991,"uid":194715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T15:00:00.000Z","msg":